-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
------1. Wap in c to enter a no and check ifit is a palindrome number or not ->>> Algorithm:-----------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Start.
2. Read any three digit number
3. Copy num to n.
4. check while condition for while loop.
5. Copy n%10 to rem.
6. Copy n/10 to n.
7. copy ((rev*10)+rem).
8. Display the value of rev.
9. Check  if codition if num equal to rev or not
if True
  Display Palindrome number.
if False
  Display NOt an Palindrome number.
10. Stop.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------End of 1 program Algoritm.----------------------------------------------------------------------
